      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a reliable companion for your daily commute? This vehicle is in fair condition and ready to get you where you need to go! It shows some honest signs of its journey so far, both inside and out, but it remains a solid, dependable choice for anyone seeking practical transportation at a great value. Come see why this road-tested ride still has plenty of great miles left to offer!",
